or: rgb(93, 208, 230); box-sizing: border-box;"> </section> <section style="width: 1.2em; height: 1.2em; margin-top: -0.88em; line-height: 1.2em; background-color: rgb(106, 226, 250); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 23px; box-sizing: border-box;">
